I have her lipstick!

95
00:03:46,458 --> 00:03:48,333
<i>But Buster knew that lipstick</i>

96
00:03:48,375 --> 00:03:50,750
<i>wasn't the only thing</i>
<i>she'd be without.</i>

97
00:03:50,792 --> 00:03:55,667
<i>So, after she was released to</i>
<i>await trial under house arrest,</i>

98
00:03:55,709 --> 00:03:59,333
<i>he made sure she was able</i>
<i>to catch up on what she missed.</i>

99
00:03:59,375 --> 00:04:01,500
This is the same scene
I came back to

100
00:04:01,542 --> 00:04:04,417
