<i>George Sr. should move out,</i>

103
00:04:11,625 --> 00:04:14,583
<i>in order to make</i>
<i>their fake divorce look real.</i>

104
00:04:14,625 --> 00:04:16,583
After the trial,
you can move back in.

105
00:04:16,625 --> 00:04:19,333
It's only a trial separation.

106
00:04:19,375 --> 00:04:21,500
(laughs):
I made a pun.

107
00:04:21,542 --> 00:04:22,500
(chuckles)

108
00:04:22,542 --> 00:04:24,750
Even in this time of stress.

109
00:04:24,792 --> 00:04:27,333
You think you're gonna be okay,
alone with Buster?

110
00:04:27,375 --> 00:04:29,542
If I need a moment to myself,
I'll step out on the balcony.

111
00:04:29,583 --> 00:04:31,291
Your ankle bracelet--
it's gonna go off.

112
00:04:31,333 --> 00:04:32,917
