practically delirious.

115
00:04:40,792 --> 00:04:41,834
(Buster sobs)

116
00:04:41,875 --> 00:04:43,834
<i>There was one bright spot</i>

117
00:04:43,875 --> 00:04:45,834
<i>when they simultaneously</i>
<i>stumbled on a term</i>

