key witness.

174
00:06:54,208 --> 00:06:56,542
Star witness.

175
00:06:56,583 --> 00:06:58,625
And are you
threatening yourself?

176
00:06:58,667 --> 00:07:00,125
Maybe I am.

177
00:07:00,166 --> 00:07:04,291
<i>And losing confidence</i>
<i>in her star witness,</i>

178
00:07:04,333 --> 00:07:06,709
<i>Lucille decided to take</i>
<i>a few keepsakes with her,</i>

179
00:07:06,750 --> 00:07:10,291
<i>in case things didn't</i>
<i>go her way.</i>

180
00:07:11,667 --> 00:07:13,208
<i>And that's when she discovered</i>

181
00:07:13,250 --> 00:07:15,667
