for tomorrow.

187
00:07:28,667 --> 00:07:31,208
<i>Actually, they'd claimed</i>
<i>those things years earlier</i>

188
00:07:31,250 --> 00:07:34,000
<i>when she was having</i>
<i>a sunspot checked.</i>

189
00:07:34,041 --> 00:07:35,583
<i>But she was right</i>
<i>to worry about</i>

190
00:07:35,625 --> 00:07:37,166
<i>the turnout for the trial.</i>

191
00:07:37,208 --> 00:07:40,041
