a strategy for us.

194
00:07:43,792 --> 00:07:45,917
Oh. It's us now?

195
00:07:45,959 --> 00:07:48,208
Well, we have Lucille Austero.

196
00:07:48,250 --> 00:07:49,750
She's the only one who showed.

197
00:07:49,792 --> 00:07:51,709
I don't think
that is good for us.

198
00:07:51,750 --> 00:07:52,875
Nonsense.

199
00:07:52,917 --> 00:07:54,333
-She owns the company now.
-Mm-hmm.

200
00:07:54,375 --> 00:07:56,542
She's got as much to lose
as I do.

201
00:07:56,583 --> 00:07:58,166
And she's a dear friend.

202
00:07:58,208 --> 00:07:59,750
I'll do it myself though.

203
00:07:59,792 --> 00:08:01,333
I need this to go well.

204
00:08:01,375 --> 00:08:04,667
<i>And so it was Lucille</i>
<i>who did the questioning</i>

205
00:08:04,709 --> 00:08:07,250
<i>of her new star witness,</i>
<i>Lucille 2.</i>

206
00:08:07,291 --> 00:08:09,834
Thank you so much
for coming to be my witness.

207
00:08:09,875 --> 00:08:11,959
You're such
a large shareholder...

208
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:13,667
Oh...

209
00:08:13,709 --> 00:08:15,291
(chuckles):
I've made a pun.

210
00:08:15,333 --> 00:08:18,583
