a Rorschach test.

227
00:08:52,125 --> 00:08:54,667
(chuckles): Not that there'd be
anyone to see it.

228
00:08:54,709 --> 00:08:56,333
So, as I was saying...

229
00:08:56,375 --> 00:08:57,959
<i>But unfortunately,</i>

230
00:08:58,000 --> 00:09:00,208
<i>their 30-year</i>
<i>passive-aggressive dance</i>

231
00:09:00,250 --> 00:09:02,125
